At the same time certain formalities, approaching in character to those of such a trial, had to be gone through before the censor affixed his nota. The person incriminated was summoned, formally accused (cp. si qui contra dicere vellet, ἓ 134), and allowed the services of an advocate, before the censors pronounced sentence.
